{"tid":1737101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"理大挾持人質事件","createTime":"2019-11-19T01:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T01:57:31.000Z","uid":128391,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7a65b41cd7de8275cec4b72d1513aeffba090f","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"理大人質事件經多日後終於落幕。日前有暴徒因不滿只有自己失業決定堵路阻人返工，於理大堵塞馬路並挾持參觀理大的香港人作人質。警察到場後嘗試攻入理大營救人質，但暴徒竟以人質作要脅，要求其他人質死守理大，無可奈何，大量人質被迫與警察發生衝突。人質事件發生一日後，警察仍未成功營救人質，於是示威者自發組團營救人質（手足）。但因修例風波，示威者與警察不和，於是在尖沙咀發生衝突，暴徒趁亂逃離理大。人質自行離開理大後被警察誤認為暴徒而拘捕。"},{"pid":"22ea537517b1db337ec6d0dcb25c882b9e6609f1","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"4dcede35b633e4a4ef56bf729499be8edb79c69f","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:11:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"ba9ca2459219498069a09059278ff51f59366060","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:11:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"380230b7cb520e1217d504d72ab8c2844e5a907b","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:11:48.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7a28b02db5d96175b9a084ad3393c1664e025817","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"83c76a69ded53853a124b0d16d5224cce812a6f5","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:12:14.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9360a0f580a2da82ba1fb06c36c2803292ae3bc3","tid":1737101,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b38f6a83d0fe26cf8715fc8110da3ab62a3ac95","tid":1737101,"uid":128391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T01:12:29.000Z","msg":"7"}